<h1 class="article-header__title">Facebook slams Apple&#039;s new privacy measures in full-page newspaper ads</h1>
<span class="article-header__intro">"We're standing up to Apple for small businesses everywhere."</span>
<div class="article-header__details">
<div class="article-header__authors">
<span class="article-header__author"><a href="/author/Stephen%20Warwick">Stephen Warwick</a></span>  </div>
<time class="article-header__time" itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2020-12-16T05:46:46-05:00" title="Wed, 16 Dec 2020 05:46:46 -0500">
16 Dec 2020
</time>
